messages.content:
Hello! I'm your AI booking assistant. I can help you schedule appointments for various services including:

• **Consultation** (30-60 minutes)
• **Therapy Session** (60 minutes)
• **Workshop** (90-120 minutes)
• **Meeting** (30-60 minutes)
• **Business Consultation** (45-90 minutes)
• **Creative Session** (60-90 minutes)

How can I help you today?
You can simply tell me what you need, like:
• 'I need a consultation tomorrow at 10 AM'
• 'Book a therapy session for next Monday'
• 'Schedule a workshop for next week'

**Quick Actions:**
• Book a meeting
• Show available slots
